33#define EXTRACTS_BIT(reg, bit) ((reg >> bit) & 0x1)

70struct internal_id_info_t {
71 union {
72 amd_code_t amd;
73 centaur_code_t centaur;
74 intel_code_t intel;
75 } code;
76 uint64_t bits;
77 int score; // detection (matchtable) score
78 int32_t cache_mask[NUM_CACHE_TYPES];
79};
